{"tid":556762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大埔翻巴士】部份死者名單","createTime":"2018-02-10T17:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T18:44:44.000Z","uid":73915,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"60b839826f14e4b0556ff0be316e083f32c69e33","tid":556762,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T17:26:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180211/57818635\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180211%2F57818635&d=cNJeB2n5zIIAFieHs6AH8jA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=267ef5c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180211%2F57818635&h=16c8fba9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180211/57818635</a><br />\n<br />\n大埔公路發生奪命車禍，造成18人死亡，包括15男3女，另外64名傷者中，9男1女情況危殆、20男情況嚴重、31男2女情況穩定、1男已出院，以下為部份死者名單：<br />\n<br />\n15男3女死者部份名單<br />\n<br />\n1,周文齊（女 55歲）<br />\n2,李炳林（男 67歲）<br />\n3,趙錦鑄（男 58歲）<br />\n4,姓鄧（男 65歲）<br />\n5,劉美蓮（女 61歲）<br />\n6,王玉麟（男 60歲）<br />\n7,李思錫（男 66歲）<br />\n8,黃兆良（男 50歲）<br />\n9,田天松（男 62歲）<br />\n10,丘小牛（男 61歲）<br />\n11,黃伙娣（男 58歲）<br />\n12,張朝偉（男 65歲）<br />\n13,鄭帶勝（男 61歲）<br />\n14,陳賢妹（女 62歲）<br />\n另3男1女未確認身份"},{"pid":"4b7276f926f20c14c82eb0b3b9b8c073baffcca8","tid":556762,"uid":156422,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T17:28:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c18fb7ceb155a80188ff81312c2c7fff40cbd95","tid":556762,"uid":29880,"like":7,"dislike":10,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T17:28:41.000Z","msg":"全部廢老<br />\n<br />\n利申:早就搬離厚德邨"},{"pid":"b71cb9c67b8361b58af31169f4106df26a2e5460","tid":556762,"uid":97814,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T17:29:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6619b2e004fbd43a831e83f2d2da3726ef72e042","tid":556762,"uid":36178,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"rep